<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Skillmate</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
        }
        .header img {
            max-width: 120px;
        }
        .content {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .content h1 {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #333;
        }
        .content p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            color: #555;
        }
        .link {
            color: #00c853;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .button-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .button {
            background-color: #00c853;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 16px;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        .footer {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #999;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding-top: 10px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eaeaea;
        }
        .social-icons {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .social-icons img {
            margin: 0 5px;
            width: 24px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <!-- Header with Logo -->
        <div class="header">
            <img src="https://career.skillmate.ai/svg/skillmate.svg" alt="Skillmate Logo">
        </div>
        <!-- Header with Logo -->
        <!-- <div class="center">
            <img src="https://career.skillmate.ai/svg/skillmate.svg" alt="Skillmate Logo">
        </div> -->

        <!-- Email Content -->
        <div class="content">
            <h1>Hi Team,</h1>
            <p>
                We have received a new mentor registration form submission. Please review and verify the details provided to ensure compliance with our mentorship program requirements.
                Name:<%= mentor %>, Email: <%= email %>
            </p>
            <p>
                Verification Process:
            </p>
            <p>
               1. Log in to the admin portal and access the pending mentor applications.
            </p>
            <p>
               2. Review the mentor’s information for accuracy and completeness.
            </p>
            <p>
               3. If approved, notify the mentor of successful verification.
            </p>
            <p>
                For any discrepancies or further verification steps, please follow up with the applicant directly.
            </p>
            <p>
                Thank you for helping maintain the integrity of our mentor community!
            </p>
           
            <p>Best Regards,</p>
            <p><strong>The Skillmate Team</strong></p>
            <p>PS - I personally look at all emails. Look forward to hearing from you :)</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Divider and Additional Information -->
        <hr>
        <div class="content">
            <p>
                We are here to support you every step of the way. If you have any questions or need assistance, please don’t hesitate to reach out to us at
            </p>
            <div class="button-container">
                <a href="https://skillmate.ai" class="button">skillmate.ai</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Social Media Links -->
        <div class="social-icons">
            <a href="https://www.facebook.com/skillmateofficial"><img src="https://pngimg.com/uploads/facebook_logos/facebook_logos_PNG19752.png" alt="Facebook"></a>
            <a href="https://www.instagram.com/skillmateofficial"><img src="https://pngimg.com/uploads/instagram/instagram_PNG10.png" alt="Instagram"></a>
            <a href="https://twitter.com/skillmate257345"><img src="https://pngimg.com/uploads/twitter/twitter_PNG9.png" alt="Twitter"></a>
            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/skillmate-official/"><img src="https://pngimg.com/uploads/linkedIn/linkedIn_PNG2.png" alt="LinkedIn"></a>
        </div>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Thank you for choosing Skillmate. We look forward to helping you achieve your career goals.</p>
            <p>Best Regards,</p>
            <p><strong>The Skillmate Team</strong></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
